Name: Magali
AboutMe:
I graduated in 2012 and received my Bachelor degree in Applied Computer Science at the college university of Ghent. After 6 months of searching for a job, I was hired by the same college university from which I graduated, as a Junior SharePoint Developer. I began working there in January 2013.

I am working on a new intranet in SharePoint 2013 that serves as a document management system and quality management system. My project went public to all the employees in the faculty of Business and Information management (roughly 400 users) in January 2014.

Many of the questions I asked on Stack Exchange were asked to improve my project, most questions are answered and I even answered some of them myself after trying hard enough to find a solution myself.
